Apache Maven Plugins
====================

http://maven.apache.org/plugins/

Users list: users@maven.apache.org
Developers list: dev@maven.apache.org

This is a fork of Apache Maven Plugins adding the following functionality:

* Dependency to custom (forked) `doxia-doc-renderer` supporting generated TOC for FO.
* New `includeAllDescriptors` configuration to automatically build PDFs for all `*.pdf.xml` descriptors in the configured `siteDirectory`.
* Adds a `fop-userconfig.xml` that includes all system fonts to make them available to the FO stylesheet.

